Itsy-bitsy spider (Itsy-bitsy)
Climbed up the water spout (up the water spout)

Down came the rain
And washed the spider out (washed the spider out)

Out came the sun
And dried up all the rain (dried up all the rain)

And the itsy-bitsy spider
Climbed up the spout again
Come you all...
Look at that spider go..

And the itsy-bitsy spider climbed up the door again
Climb, Climb, Climb, Climb, Climb
